Package: sane.gesis
Title: Create and Install From MiniCRAN Repositories for Offline Package Management
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for creating portable miniCRAN repositories and
    installing packages in offline or restricted network environments.
    Automatically detects package dependencies from R scripts, Quarto files,
    and R Markdown documents, downloads all required packages, and bundles
    them into a compressed repository that can be transferred and installed
    without internet access.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
